      "title": "1 hour & 20 minutes power cut for next two days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The power cut schedule of 1 hour and 20 minutes for Monday (15) and Tuesday (16) was approved today, the Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka (PUCSL) said.",
        "Accordingly,\u00a0 1 hour and 20 minutes power shedding will be imposed on groups A,B,C,D,E,F,G,H,I,J,K,L,P,Q,R,S,T,U,V and W from 5.00pm to 9.00pm."
      ],
